Class Actor

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.image.ImageView
        • model.Actor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Animal, CrocHead, Crocodile, End, Log, Obstacle, Turtle, WetTurtle

    public abstract class Actor
extends javafx.scene.image.ImageView
    This abstract class extends ImageView and allows for other classes to implement its act method. It manipulates ImageView by moving it around in the GUI and check for any collisions.
    Since:
    2020-12-12
    Version:
    final 6.9
    Author:
